                                <expan>unt<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan> insigel und klagt <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>H<ex>er</ex>man,</expan>
<expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan> vicarier bey uns; nu
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>H<ex>er</ex>man</expan> den brief <expan>höre<ex>n</ex></expan> und
                        lesen lassen und <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> spricht, er wöll ew
                                <expan>selb<ex>er</ex></expan> ein <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
                        darauf <expan>schreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
